import { Box, TextField } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const CreateContact = () => {
  return (
    <Box sx={{
        width : '70%',
        height : '80vh',
        display : 'flex',
        alignItems : 'center',
        justifyContent : 'center',
        alignContent : 'center',
        border : 1,
        borderColor : 'lightgrey'
        }}>
        <Box component={'form'} sx={{width : '80%'}}>
            <TextField name='firstName' label={'FirstName'} variant={'outlined'} sx={{width : '80%'}} />           
        </Box>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default CreateContact
